BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:CANCELLED - Community Fix-It Night at Northgate Community Center
LOCATION:10510 5th Ave NE\, Seattle\, WA 98125
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T163000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260327T190000
X-MICROSOFT-CDO-ALLDAYEVENT:FALSE
URL:https://seattlereconomy.org/event/fix-it-night-at-northgate-communit
 y-center/
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Building Name / Room Number / Site";ID=20637;
 TYPE=MultiLine:Northgate Community Center
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Description";ID=18998;TYPE=MultiLine:Jo
 in Seattle REconomy for a night of repair and skill-building at the Nort
 hgate Community Center! The NE Fixers program\, supported by the Departm
 ent of Neighborhoods&#8217\; Matching Fund\, aims to share repair skills
  within local communities.During these free events\, community volunteer
 s will be on hand to offer their skills to help fix things like lamps\, 
 small appliances\, clothing items\, small furniture\, and other items\, 
 as well as to sharpen and maintain tools such as garden shears and prune
 rs.Anyone is welcome to attend these repair events! There will be repair
 s\, tool sharpening\, and refreshments. Sign up on our website: <a href=
 "https://seattlereconomy.org/event/fix-it-night-at-northgate-community-c
 enter/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="https://seattlereconomy.or
 g/event/fix-it-night-at-northgate-community-center/">seattlereconomy.org
 &#8230\;</a> If you are interested in being a Fixer for an event\, pleas
 e reach out to our Outreach Coordinator\, at <a href="mailto:outreach@se
 attlereconomy.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">outreach@seattlerecono
 my.org</a>. We would love to have you!
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="DON Programs";ID=15254;TYPE=CustomAsset:Neigh
 borhood Matching Fund
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Sponsoring Organization";ID=10959;TYPE=Single
 Line:Seattle REconomy
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Contact Email";ID=10949;TYPE=Email:<a href="m
 ailto:outreach@seattlereconomy.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">outre
 ach@seattlereconomy.org</a>
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Pre-Register";ID=10961;TYPE=Boolean:Yes
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Cost";ID=10963;TYPE=SingleLine:Free
DTSTAMP:20260320T133233Z
CATEGORIES:Public
