 ts and founders in Tech &amp\; Business\, as well as top investors\, to 
 gain deep insights and valuable networking.&#8203\;This event is essenti
 al for those looking to gain ideas\, experience\, and valuable connectio
 ns.&#8203\;&#8203\;&#x1F4C8\; Present Your Startup in Tech &amp\; Busine
 ss:&#8203\;Showcase your startup in the Tech &amp\; Business fields! Sen
 d your pitch deck to <a href="mailto:contact.us@startupvalley.club" targ
 et="_blank" rel="noopener">contact.us@startupvalley.club</a> and seize t
 he opportunity to impress both the audience and investors!&#8203\;Also\,
  you need to fill out the application to participate as a pitcher/speake
 r at the event.&#8203\;Apply now!&#8203\;&#8203\;&#x1F4BC\; We Welcome N
 ew Investors:&#8203\;We invite investors to our event to expand their ne
 twork\, get acquainted with new startups\, evaluate them\, provide feedb
 ack\, participate in discussions\, and gain access to a database of fres
 h startups from around the world.If you&#39\;d like access to a database
  of promising startup projects and additional benefits from Startup Vall
 ey\, please fill out this application\, and our team will contact you.&#
 8203\;Who you will meet at the event:&#8203\;Founders&#8203\;Investors o
 r VC companies&#8203\;Marketers\, Salespeople\, Business Advisers&#8203
 \;Industry Disruptors&#8203\;AI Experts&#8203\;Entrepreneurs from Europe
 \, Asia\, and the United Kingdom&#8203\;&#8203\;Requirements for attendee
 s:&#8203\;21+ years old&#8203\;Neat appearance&#8203\;Good mood&#8203\;1
  drink bought at the bar (non-alcohol works too)&#8203\;&#x1F91D\; The v
 enue\, where we host our events\, is our partner. To continue hosting ev
 ents at this location\, please consider purchasing 1-2 drinks at the bar
 . Thank you.&#8203\;&#8203\;Time:&#8203\;Event time: 7:00 PM to 10:00 PM
 &#8203\;Pitch time: 8:40 PM to 9:20 PM&#8203\;&#8203\;&#x1F39F\; Join ou
