 ubmission Form Template
X-TRUMBA-CUSTOMFIELD;NAME="Event Description";ID=18998;TYPE=MultiLine:Jo
 in us for a feast for your senses at our November Open Studios! Wander t
 hrough artist workspaces\, discover art in every medium &#8212\; from fi
 ne to funky and everything in between &#8212\; and enjoy bonfires\, musi
 c\, and a little mischief along the way.Whether you&#8217\;re here to sp
 ark a new idea\, meet your favorite artist\, or just sip something cozy 
 by the fire\, we&#8217\;d love to see you!Saturday\, Nov 86&#8211\;9 PME
 quinox Studios6555 5th Ave S &#8212\; Sunny West Georgetown (near Michig
 an St &amp\; 5th Ave S)Come say hi\, explore\, and soak in the creativit
 y. See you there!
